snippet: Indianapolis Colts center Khaled Holmes was ruled out for Monday’s showdown with the undefeated Carolina Panthers.
abstract: Indianapolis Colts center Khaled Holmes will not play in upcoming game against Carolina Panthers due to minor neck injury; other football news noted.
